<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 12:24:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国称印度无权在阿鲁纳恰尔邦进行开发</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，印度无权在其所谓的藏南地区进行开发，回应路透社关于新德里计划加快边境邦阿鲁纳恰尔邦水电项目的报道。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>波兰称制裁导致白俄罗斯卡车入境速度放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-says-entry-trucks-belarus-slowed-by-sanctions-2024-07-10/</link><description>波兰海关发言人周三表示，在明斯克表示华沙已停止允许卡车过境后，新的制裁措施导致卡车从白俄罗斯过境进入波兰的速度放缓。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:37:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-says-entry-trucks-belarus-slowed-by-sanctions-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国最大汽车制造商上汽集团因销售低迷而重组领导层</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-biggest-automaker-saic-reshuffles-leadership-amid-sluggish-sales-2024-07-10/</link><description>上汽集团总裁王晓秋在领导层改组中当选为董事长，这家中国最大的汽车制造商正在应对国内市场销售低迷和欧盟面临的高额关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-biggest-automaker-saic-reshuffles-leadership-amid-sluggish-sales-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥海军警告双重用途化学品正在增加冰毒产量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-navy-warns-dual-use-chemicals-are-boosting-meth-production-2024-07-10/</link><description>四名海军官员告诉路透社，管理该国最大港口的墨西哥海军官员越来越担心用于生产甲基苯丙胺和芬太尼等合成药物的不受监管的“双重用途”化学品的流量不断增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-navy-warns-dual-use-chemicals-are-boosting-meth-production-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国与巴西试行牛肉追溯计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</link><description>官方媒体周三表示，全球最大的牛肉进口国中国和最大的牛肉供应国巴西将设立一项试点计划，作为使牛肉生产更加可持续的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>禽流感病毒株：它们在全球哪些地方传播？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bird-flu-strains-spread-around-globe-2024-07-10/</link><description>今年，禽流感在美国奶牛中出现前所未有的传播，公共卫生官员对此保持警惕。该国四名乳制品工人的检测结果也呈阳性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/bird-flu-strains-spread-around-globe-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着投资者押注政府支出，太空初创公司的资金持续复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/space-startups-funding-continues-recover-investors-bet-government-spending-2024-07-10/</link><description>英国投资公司 Seraphim Space 的数据显示，4 月至 6 月，太空初创公司吸引了 24.1 亿美元的全球投资，标志着融资连续第三个季度增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/space-startups-funding-continues-recover-investors-bet-government-spending-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国避免通货紧缩，市场平静，新西兰鸽派</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-10/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>泽连斯基返回华盛顿表示感谢并建立关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/zelenskiy-returns-washington-say-thanks-build-relationships-2024-07-10/</link><description>乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽林斯基周三返回美国国会，巩固与议员的关系，议员们将对乌克兰未来的援助进行投票，并感谢他们自 2022 年 2 月俄罗斯入侵以来已批准的 1750 亿美元资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/zelenskiy-returns-washington-say-thanks-build-relationships-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车第二季度交付量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-deliveries-fall-second-quarter-2024-07-10/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，今年第二季度集团交付量较去年同期下降3.8%，但仍预计全年将小幅回升。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-deliveries-fall-second-quarter-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国称黄岩岛水域“非常好”，驳回菲律宾的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</link><description>就在菲律宾指责中国渔民破坏海洋环境几个月后，中国关于黄岩岛争议渔场周围海域的一份报告认为该海域水质优良，珊瑚礁健康。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾空军参加在澳大利亚举行的多国军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-air-force-joins-multi-nation-war-games-australia-2024-07-10/</link><description>菲律宾空军周三抵达澳大利亚北部，这是其六十年来的首次海外部署，与美国和澳大利亚军队一起进行战斗训练，之际南海与中国的紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:26:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-air-force-joins-multi-nation-war-games-australia-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，随着消费下滑，中国第二季度GDP复苏可能失去动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-gdp-recovery-likely-lost-steam-q2-consumption-sags-2024-07-10/</link><description>由于消费需求低迷，中国经济第二季度同比增长可能为 5.1%，较前三个月的强劲开局有所放缓，这使得人们对北京需要推出更多刺激措施的预期仍不减。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-gdp-recovery-likely-lost-steam-q2-consumption-sags-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国加强对四大会计师事务所的审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dials-up-scrutiny-big-four-audit-firms-after-evergrande-probe-sources-say-2024-07-10/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国财政部正在对四大审计公司为本土企业所做的工作进行更严格的检查，原因是担心审计机构在发现企业不当行为方面做得不够。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dials-up-scrutiny-big-four-audit-firms-after-evergrande-probe-sources-say-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>副部长表示波兰将采取必要措施结束白俄罗斯边境危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-will-do-what-is-needed-end-belarus-border-crisis-says-deputy-minister-2024-07-10/</link><description>一名国防部副部长表示，波兰将尽一切努力解决其与白俄罗斯边境的移民危机，华沙正在权衡可能包括关闭边境在内的选择。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-will-do-what-is-needed-end-belarus-border-crisis-says-deputy-minister-2024-07-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>